                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 893.51/887.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">American Minister</gloss> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Peking</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1912-05-16T21:00:00+08:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 16, 1912—9 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>An advance of 3,000,000 taels will be made May 17 by the groups to the Chinese
                    Government, which agrees to supervision of expenditures.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Calhoun.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
